🚀 Production Deployment — v1.0.0

PokéMarket is now live at https://game.crdsystems.online

Infrastructure

Deployed to Ubuntu 24 VPS
Nginx reverse proxy serving static frontend and proxying /api/* to Express backend
PM2 process manager with auto-restart on reboot
SSL/HTTPS via Let's Encrypt with Cloudflare DNS
Stack

Frontend: React + Vite (built to /dist, served by Nginx)
Backend: Express.js API running on port 3001 via PM2
Database: PostgreSQL via Supabase (connection pooler)
Auth: JWT access/refresh token rotation with bcrypt password hashing
